Interface Vars<T>

  • Type Parameters:
    T - The type of the properties.
    All Superinterfaces:
    java.lang.Iterable<T>, Vals<T>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractVariables

    public interface Vars<T>
extends Vals<T>
    A list of mutable properties. Use the Vals.onChange(Action) method to register a listener for changes to the list.
